{"tid":482964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推翻NASA理論】 火星表面的「水」是「流動沙粒」","createTime":"2017-11-28T16:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T19:10:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9953cac31b11c4199143f17aec4f59a35854db33","tid":482964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"// 美國太空總署 (NASA) 近年公佈發現火星或有液態水，但一項新發表的研究結果則指，這可能只是「美麗的誤會」。 <br />\n<br />\n當時 NASA 的研究指，發現火星表面上有「季節性坡紋線 (RSL)」，在這些溝谷隨季節冷暖變化而出現的流動物質，就是液態水。 <br />\n<br />\n但亞利桑那大學 (The University of Arizona) 研究團隊，分析了在火星表面的 151 條坡紋線，發現只有在斜度大於 27 度時，才觀測到物質流動。 <br />\n<br />\n如果是液態水，在斜度 27 度以下應該會繼續流動，推測流動物質並非液態水，而更有可能是沙粒及泥土等。 <br />\n<br />\n團隊相信，火星上或有水存在，但整體環境難以讓生物生存。// <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/762339820624755/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F762339820624755%2F&d=DstuGdSe1pRyRRMD08SOszPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0d0b7e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/762339820624755/</a>"},{"pid":"921495b44e7a796a5359a70226f495dd1d2322c8","tid":482964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb12068e528ec55188cf7c3481f35b8ea4b267bf","tid":482964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ebbb45721a07705077a5aafcc319ae771b8c4","tid":482964,"uid":50060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk: 屌你咩咁我d project 點啊 唔緊要 迫d員工整隻飛船比我上去睇下係咪真係無水先"},{"pid":"34b4ba5964ed201af91878db5ff9c752b3c479e5","tid":482964,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26526f68721a322373674ff0ddcc607daa7c68f","tid":482964,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:07:35.000Z","msg":"諗到如果有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n因為地球就黎滅亡 所以派左最後既人類去火星<br />\n<br />\n但去到先發現原來乜都無 水都無滴都幾絕望"},{"pid":"f7b2faa01b1ba7837482281b5b68e4524db84bd2","tid":482964,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T19:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗到如果有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n因為地球就黎滅亡 所以派左最後既人類去火星<br />\n<br />\n但去到先發現原來乜都無 水都無滴都幾絕望</blockquote><br />\nInterstellar?"}]}